{"tid":1389904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重要！麻煩大家入黎傾一傾黎緊嘅方向！","createTime":"2019-07-31T04:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T05:56:53.000Z","uid":9803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2b26d9256a0faa932e419e6b952398b21507898e","tid":1389904,"uid":9803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:20:21.000Z","msg":"依家有兩大堆人<br />\n<br />\n一堆係覺得要有真雙普選先至應該有獨立調查委員會<br />\n如果唔係嘅話依家成立左只會草草了事<br />\n以後都唔提仲衰過無<br />\n<br />\n另一堆係覺得依家已經要有 唔理點都成立左先<br />\n<br />\n因為黎緊行程好密 唔想每次都淨係聽至林鄭下台同埋香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n要對準政權！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔理好醜叫左先算<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔叫住 叫左其他口號先"},{"pid":"e8d9751da7f38345c6b9b664091d07e611949208","tid":1389904,"uid":9803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推"},{"pid":"70e22517239c9844749351426e0feff229a6f6ab","tid":1389904,"uid":9803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:27:51.000Z","msg":"我知義士同尋晚嘅事好緊要<br />\n但係黎緊有好多行程 要勝利先真正幫到義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9WVyYS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9WVyYS.png&h=0b3c9620&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cL6Zgcc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcL6Zgcc.png&h=961c2d10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rjfy45x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frjfy45x.png&h=2f85ff32&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jQuW2Se.pn